69f-ee9e-41a9-9d4e-2cc4781bff05\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d43f4385-5e9b-426a-8ebd-1a2b071ec9b1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4047831b-a284-4d8a-88f5-1a268da64553\">이러한 실천 방법들은 머리로는 당연하고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b4971609-fe61-43a6-b707-12d3bc6d5c6d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6d556b02-5da9-48b8-b97f-ea1ecc33ebc8\">상식적으로 알고 있지만,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6cf197e4-d842-4de0-965c-aeae35b3a3a8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-803328b4-5c54-486b-af11-4ac2f73d00b2\">몸으로 실천하는 것은 어려움이 따를 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e4bf0d00-a431-435b-97c5-345fa6433e9e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-fd3b69ef-6bc3-4fc9-bdad-76bda42f6d71\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9f3f032d-db4d-41f8-bd18-f8d84b0768d7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-18268c77-0a7b-4501-b964-be69158147d3\">건강한 몸을 지키기 위해서는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5163f4f2-a32a-4935-a515-abd2275a7593\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6ffe56a0-a0fe-48d5-a239-fc549980c445\">몸과 마음을 조절하며</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-dbccb4e2-fd8a-458c-b513-3e9b6ea845f3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-65665d7e-8372-462e-b74d-65220c88bdb9\">균형을 유지하는 것이 필요합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --